# Backend Python (uv)

- Use **uv**, not `pip`, for dependencies in this monorepo.
- Install / lock from repo root (or with explicit `--project`):
  - Sync: `uv sync --project server --frozen --no-dev` (see [README.md](README.md) and `scripts/run.sh`).
  - Add a library: `uv add --project server <package>` (adjust flags as needed, e.g. `--dev`).
- Run Django and tests through uv, e.g. `uv run --project server python manage.py test …` (see `taskfile.sh`).
